title: Too Famous In Norway
description:
We get down and dirty this week reviewing New York's “naked bootcamps", and Dr Axe comes back as promised to give us the 101 on Traditional Chinese Medicine and how it might be able to help you on your health and fitness journey! Plus, Jillian is finally ready to share the comedy of errors that became her new years “vacay” with Too Famous In Norway.
